text: Heena Panchal is an Indian film actress and celebrity known for her works in Bollywood and Marathi. She is most famous for her item songs "Balam Bambai" and "Bevda Bevda Zalo Mi Tight". In 2019, she participated in Bigg Boss Marathi.
